M||tx|---
M||titl|Animate SVG Wrapper Instead of SVG Element
M||impa|lo
M||impa|enables hardware acceleration
M||tags|rendering, svg, css, animation, perf
M||tx|---
M|Anim|tx|Many browsers don't have hardware acceleration for CSS3 animations on SVG elements. Wrap SVG in a `<div>` and animate the wrapper instead.
M|Anim|**In|**
M|Anim|tx|```tsx
M|Anim|tx|fn LoadingSpinner() {
M|Anim|tx|return (
M|Anim|tx|<svg
M|Anim|tx|className="animate-spin"
M|Anim|tx|width="24"
M|Anim|tx|height="24"
M|Anim|tx|viewBox="0 0 24 24"
M|Anim|tx|>
M|Anim|tx|<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" />
M|Anim|tx|</svg>
M|Anim|tx|)
M|Anim|tx|}
M|Anim|tx|```
M|Anim|**Co|**
M|Anim|tx|```tsx
M|Anim|tx|fn LoadingSpinner() {
M|Anim|tx|return (
M|Anim|tx|<div className="animate-spin">
M|Anim|tx|<svg
M|Anim|tx|width="24"
M|Anim|tx|height="24"
M|Anim|tx|viewBox="0 0 24 24"
M|Anim|tx|>
M|Anim|tx|<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" />
M|Anim|tx|</svg>
M|Anim|tx|</div>
M|Anim|tx|)
M|Anim|tx|}
M|Anim|tx|```
M|Anim|tx|This applies to all CSS transforms and transitions (`transform`, `opacity`, `translate`, `scale`, `rotate`). The wrapper div allows browsers to use GPU acceleration for smoother animations.